(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 360.68 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 35785bae-c884-58cb-aab9-223b33b1d438))
(text "TI Figure 39 core is implemented: SEL0/SEL1 direct-high, 1.5k D+ pull-up, filtered VBUS, and separate rail capacitors." (at 20.32 368.3 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e9569332-1782-5ab5-99e6-80a8efdc19d9))
(text "Independent 82k/1k dividers produce about 8.4mVrms open-circuit; Q330/Q331 mute on PTT_N high, USB suspend, or codec power loss." (at 20.32 375.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ef85f549-9f03-57ce-941a-c01c45bae805))
(text "RELEASE GATE: measure MIC impedance and deviation per band; preserve mainboard PTT defaults and hard-interlock both PTT_N signals." (at 20.32 383.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ba8c1ae6-9e7c-5ee2-93c8-12762d45c023))
